    "Id": "chassisdef_king_dragon_DRG-23K2",
    "Name": "King Dragon",
    "Details": "As the -23K was deemed underperforming, the -23K2 was conceived as a quick refit to restore it to be more in line with the better performing earlier specifications of the -22E and -22K. All the PPCs were removed, instead two Large and two Medium X-Pulse Lasers were added. The result once again restored the King Dragon to its much loved position within the DCMS.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Well Balanced</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.3</color></b>",
